# CatalogService Proto Contract: CategoryTaxonomy (spec#021)
#
# NO CHANGES to shared/proto/gitstore/catalog/v1/catalog_service.proto
#
# The existing ValidateResources and AdmitResources RPCs are kind-agnostic:
# they send raw ResourceBlob bytes and the Go handler performs kind-routing
# internally. Adding CategoryTaxonomy support requires no proto changes.
#
# This file serves as the explicit record that the proto contract was reviewed
# and deliberately left unchanged.
#
# Reviewed: 2026-06-06
# Decision: No proto changes needed.
# Rationale: ResourceBlob.content carries raw YAML bytes; kind routing is a
#             Go-side concern inside cataloggrpc.Server.
